    <h2>Project</h2>

    <p>Create a portfolio is an idea for a website or an assignment due for Business Web Technologies.
    This is the first assignment web fundamentals for unit ISYS3004.</p>

    <h2>Content</h2>

    <p>Content is the most important element of a website. Written content, makes up for
    more than 90% of the Web</p>
    
    <p> The aim of design is to enhance the presentation of the content! Styling content will go a long way. 
    The portfolio website should include home, about, project, contact, and reflection page.</p>
    
    <h2>Objective</h2> 
    
    <p>The objective of this assignment is to demonstrate the fundamental web technologies used
    in the development of a portfolio website. The students will use the web technologies they
    have learned throughout the course to create a portfolio website showcasing their projects
    and skills.</p>

